title: Talking Bravo with Annaleigh Ashford
description:
We're changing things up a little bit today as we take 45 minutes to chat with actress, singer, dancer, and general superstar Annaleigh Ashford. We go deep on so many Bravo shows, starting with RHOSLC. Come listen!

Get tix to our live shows: http://watchwhatcrappens.com
